Package: BayesMFRM
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Many-Facet Rasch Models using Stan
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Jane", "Doe",
      email = "jane@example.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: An R package for Bayesian many-facet Rasch models using Stan (via cmdstanr).
    Provides an easy-to-use interface for fitting rating-scale Rasch models with multiple 
    facets (person, item, rater, etc.) and optional bias terms. Produces FACETS-style 
    outputs including fair averages, infit/outfit statistics, and bias analysis.
